WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.280
Officially, from today,

00:00:01.280 --> 00:00:03.000
March 11th, 2024,

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.360
Care assistants and Senior Care Assistants

00:00:05.360 --> 00:00:07.680
are not longer allowed to bring their dependents,

00:00:07.680 --> 00:00:08.600
including children,

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:09.700
into the UK.

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:12.240
Care Assistant and Senior Care assistants

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:15.500
switching into care within UK are also not allowed to

00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:17.380
switch with their dependent.
